The path is blocked. There might be a mechanism somewhere to

\n<Bijou>Oh, you came too? This ruin seems to be a place where some
kind of research was conducted. We might find something
interesting.

\n<Bijou>But I was thinking, suddenly this door won't open. It
doesn't seem to be sealed by any barrier magic, and there's
no keyhole either. That leads me to believe it might be
controlled by machinery...

\n<Bijou>It's okay. Even if it's old, the door mechanisms are made to
be the most durable, so they should definitely work. It
would be a problem if we got trapped by a malfunction.

\n<Bijou>Hmm... I wonder if there's a switch somewhere, like behind
the walls or pillars. Could you look for it?
A

\n<Bijou>Could you look around for a switch in any suspicious places?
Like, for example... behind a pillar?

\n<Bijou>There are monsters spawning inside too. I wonder where they
came from. Maybe there's an underground waterway or
something...

\n<Bijou>There's something written on this floor. Let's see, it's a
simple cipher. It's meant to thwart monsters with low
intelligence. Now, let's see...
\n<Bijou>...

\n<Bijou>You just need to press three more switches, it seems. Then
some sort of secret vault should appear somewhere.

\n<Bijou>If you find something that looks like it, try pressing it.
It's probably in a similar place as the last one.

\n<Bijou>My wild sensual sixth sense is telling me there's something
around here... though I have no basis for it.

\n<Bijou>Well, after years of treasure hunting, you start to get a
feel for these things
\n<Bijou>...

\n<Bijou>If I'm wrong, it'll be embarrassing, so hurry up and check
somewhere else.
\n<Bijou>Shoo, shoo! This treasure is all mine
\n<Adventurer>Aaah-!! It's hot!! So hot!

\n<Bijou>It's getting nicely roasted, isn't it? All that's left is
to slice it up and serve it on a plate

\n<Adventurer>No, not steak! I'm sorry! I'll go home now! Please forgive
me!

\n<Bijou>It's okay I'll forgive you But in exchange, leave just a
little bit of your stuff behind And by a little, you know
what I mean? Everything.
\n<Adventurer>Kugyuu...

\n<Adventurer>Ugh... I didn't expect a behemoth to be here... Maybe I
should have come earlier.
